From: Devin AI <158243242+devin-ai-integration[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 26 Jul 2025 14:31:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix frontend-backend integration: Add Basic Auth headers and
 update docker-compose

- Add Basic Auth header support to all frontend service files for tunnel authentication
- Update docker-compose.yml for improved SSL certificate handling
- Enable frontend to authenticate with tunneled backend services
- Fix CORS integration issues between frontend and backend services

This resolves the frontend-backend communication issues when using tunnel URLs
for public deployment and testing.

Co-Authored-By: ramy el-basuouny <ramy93.ali@gmail.com>
